[src:quantum-field-theory/feynman-diagram] This convention for delta-functions is not universal—some authors keep the factors of 2π in the delta functions (and in the k-integration) explicit.
[src:quantum-field-theory/feynman-diagram] The form of the propagator can be more easily found by using the equation of motion for the field.
